OL,3,CTowns 'cut off from each other' due to
OL,4,Csewer collapse
OL,6,FResidents in West Yorkshire towns have
OL,7,Fbeen told to prepare for travel
OL,8,Fdisruption due to emergency repairs to
OL,9,Fa key route through the Calder Valley.
OL,11,FThe A646 Halifax Road at Charlestown,
OL,12,Fon the western side of Hebden Bridge
OL,13,Ftown centre, is closed in both
OL,14,Fdirections after damage to sewer
OL,15,Fworkings were detected.
OL,17,FCalderdale Council say that the road
OL,18,Fwill remain closed throughout next
OL,19,Fweek (16 Dec - 22 Dec) for emergency
OL,20,Frepairs to take place.
