OL,3,CTowns 'cut off from each other' due to
OL,4,Csewer collapse
OL,6,FThey said: "This is a very busy road
OL,7,Fand significant disruption is
OL,8,Finevitable."
OL,10,FYorkshire Water has apologised for the
OL,11,Fdisruption.
OL,13,FA spokesperson said: "Unfortunately,
OL,14,Fthe repair on Halifax Road is quite
OL,15,Fcomplex. There is a collapsed culvert,
OL,16,Fwhich usually falls under council
OL,17,Fresponsibility, as well as a damaged
OL,18,Fsewer.
