OL,3,CTowns 'cut off from each other' due to
OL,4,Csewer collapse
OL,6,F"To make sure the work can be complete
OL,7,Fas soon as possible, Yorkshire Water
OL,8,Fis carrying out a repair to both
OL,9,Fassets.
OL,11,F"The issue is deep underground, so to
OL,12,Fensure the safety of our colleagues
OL,13,Fand customers, we need to shut the
OL,14,Froad for at least a week."
OL,16,F"The highways authority requires
OL,17,Fdiversion routes to follow the same
OL,18,Ftype of road that is currently closed;
OL,19,Ftherefore, the diversion is longer
OL,20,Fthan usual and may cause some
OL,21,Fdisruption."
